vatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1564796404" alt="FloppyPhoenix" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/floppyphoenix" >FloppyPhoenix</a></span> and many others for looking at this in its creation. I appreciate it.</p> <hr /> <h4><span>Art</span></h4> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">It's&nbsp;raining...</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">By&nbsp;pastarasta1</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"><img src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/526584173180485642/607020982716071957/image0.png" alt="image0.png" class="image" /></div> </div> </div> <hr /> 
